doctype html

html(lang="en")
head
	title Wikipdia Analytics
	link(rel="stylesheet" href="http://code.jquery.com/ui/1.11.4/themes/smoothness/jquery-ui.css")
	link(rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity
		|="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous")
body
	div(class='container text-right')
		form(action='login' method='POST')
			button.small(type='submit' class="btn btn-primary") Log In
	
	div.discription(class='container')
		div(class="row")
			div(class="col-xl-12")
				h1(class="text-center") Welcome to the Wikipdia Analytics
	div(class='container')
		div(class="row my-1")
			div(class="col-md-12")
				h3 Introduction
	div(class='container')
		div(class="card bg-light mb-3")
			div(class="card-body")
				p 
					| This Wikipedia Analytic Website will provide detailed analysis on the Wiki revision history data.
					| New users are allowed to create an account with specific information required, after the creation, 
					| you are allowed to use you account to login. What you can see on the main page contains the Overall Analytic, 
					| which the top research results of 6 different aspect will be demonstrated with graphs. User can select how mang top
					| results to be seen. The main page also has the Individual Analytic which the user can select one article per time
					| to see the information related to the revision made on that specific article. Another functionality is the Author 
					| Analytic, which allows the user to find the information of revision history based on the user names. Some example
					| can be seen below:
	div(class='container')
		div(class="row my-1")
			div(class="col-md-12")
				h3 Example
	div(class='container')
		div(class="card bg-light mb-3")
			div(class="card-body")
				img(src='image/image1.png' style="width:100%;height:500px")
			div(class="card-body")
				img(src='image/image2.png' style="width:100%;height:620px")



	div(class='container')
		div(class="text-center")
			form(method='POST' action='signin')
				button(type='submit' class="btn btn-block btn-primary btn-lg") Sign Up
		div(class="text-center")
			form(action='login' method='POST')
				button(type='submit' class="btn btn-block btn-success btn-lg") Log in
		div(class="text-center")
			form(action='resetpage' method='Post')
				button(type='submit' class="btn btn-block btn-secondary btn-lg") Reset Passward